Fall back to the Mountain!

3
03:51:47,310 --> 03:51:48,728
Fall back!

4
03:51:52,523 --> 03:51:53,773
AZOG [IN BLACK SPEECH]:

5
03:52:00,156 --> 03:52:02,158
[HORN BLOWING]

6
03:52:31,271 --> 03:52:32,814
KILI:
I will not hide...

7
03:52:33,064 --> 03:52:37,568
...behind a wall of stone while
others fight our battles for us!

8
03:52:41,281 --> 03:52:43,700
It is not in my blood, Thorin.

9
03:52:48,496 --> 03:52:49,872
No.

10
03:52:50,123 --> 03:52:51,541
It is not.

11
03:52:53,626 --> 03:52:55,837
We are sons of Durin.

12
03:52:58,840 --> 03:53:00,341
And Durin's Folk...

13
03:53:01,676 --> 03:53:04,137
...do not flee from a fight.

14
03:53:27,076 --> 03:53:30,955
I have no right to ask this of any of you.

15
03:53:35,960 --> 03:53:37,837
But will you follow me...

16
03:53:39,255 --> 03:53:40,965
...one last time?

17
